msgstr "IoT-järjestelmä ei toimi Odoo-päivityksen jälkeen"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:50
msgid ""
"If the issue persists, :ref:`update its image <iot/updating_iot/image-code>` "
