"program <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` and :ref:`reinstalling the virtual IoT "
"package <iot/windows-iot/installation>`."
msgstr ""
"Jos ongelma jatkuu, :ref:`päivitä sen kuva <iot/updating_iot/image-code>` "
"flashaamalla IoT-laatikon kortti tai :ref:`poistamalla Windowsin "
"virtuaalinen IoT-ohjelma <iot/windows_iot/uninstall>` ja :ref:`asentamalla "
"virtuaalinen IoT-paketti uudelleen <iot/windows-iot/installation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:57
msgid ""
"The IoT system's homepage can be accessed using its IP address but not the "
