msgid "Potential causes include the following:"
msgstr "Mahdollisia syitä ovat seuraavat:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:85
msgid ""
"The database doesn't meet the :ref:`eligibility requirements <iot/"
"https_certificate_iot/iot-eligibility>` for generating an :ref:`HTTPS "
"certificate <iot/connect/https_certificate>`."
msgstr ""
"Tietokanta ei täytä :ref:`kelpoisuusvaatimuksia <iot/https_certificate_iot/"
"iot-eligibility>` :ref:`HTTPS-varmenteen <iot/connect/https_certificate>` "
"luomiseksi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:88
msgid ""
"The firewall is preventing the HTTPS certificate from generating correctly. "
"In this case, deactivate the firewall until the certificate is successfully "
"generated."
msgstr ""
"Palomuuri estää HTTPS-varmenteen luomisen oikein. Poista tässä tapauksessa "
"palomuuri käytöstä, kunnes varmenne on onnistuneesti luotu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:92
msgid ""
"Some devices, such as routers with a built-in firewall, can prevent the "
"HTTPS certificate from generating."
msgstr ""
"Jotkin laitteet, kuten reitittimet, joissa on sisäänrakennettu palomuuri, "
"voivat estää HTTPS-varmenteen luomisen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:96
msgid "Errors"
msgstr "Virheet"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:98
msgid ""
"A specific error code is displayed on the IoT system's homepage if any "
"issues occur during the generation or reception of the :ref:`HTTPS "
"certificate <iot/connect/https_certificate>`."
msgstr ""
"Tietty virhekoodi näytetään IoT-järjestelmän etusivulla, jos :ref:`HTTPS-"
"varmenteen <iot/connect/https_certificate>` luonnissa tai vastaanotossa "
"ilmenee ongelmia."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:102
msgid ""
"When you access the IoT system's homepage, it automatically checks for an "
"HTTPS certificate and attempts to generate one if it is missing. If an error "
"appears, refresh the page to see if the issue is resolved."
msgstr ""
"Kun käytät IoT-järjestelmän kotisivua, se tarkistaa automaattisesti HTTPS-"
"varmenteen ja yrittää luoda sellaisen, jos se puuttuu. Jos virhe ilmestyy, "
"päivitä sivu nähdäksesi, onko ongelma ratkaistu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:107
msgid "Missing credentials"
msgstr "Puuttuvat tunnistetiedot"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:109
msgid ""
"The contract and/or database :abbr:`UUID (Universal Unique Identifier)` is "
"missing from the IoT."
msgstr ""
"Sopimus ja/tai tietokannan :abbr:`UUID (yleisesti yksilöllinen tunniste)` "
"puuttuu IoT:sta."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_advanced/troubleshooting.rst:111
msgid ""
"Verify that both values are correctly configured. To update "
"them, :ref:`access the IoT box's <iot/iot-box/homepage>` or :ref:`Windows "
"virtual IoT's homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>`, click the :icon:`fa-"
